4. cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) - The paper deals with the problem of autonomous agents searching for targets of interest, which is a core problem in multiagent systems. 
5. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) - Although not directly related to computer vision, the paper deals with the problem of searching for targets of interest in large-scale environments, which can be aided by computer vision techniques.
